learning_outcomes.en:
The student:
1) can use correctly French vocabulary and grammatical forms as well as French academic expressions;
2) is able to express points of view on complex subjects in a clear and well-structured text;
3) can write clear, smoothly-flowing texts in an appropriate style for a bachelor’s thesis and present an issue with logical structure.

learning_outcomes.et:
Aine edukalt läbinud üliõpilane:
1) tunneb prantsuse akadeemilise stiili põhilisi iseärasusi leksikaalsest, süntaktilisest ja tekstilisest aspektist;
2) suudab kirjutada kohases stiilis ja keeleliselt korrektse bakalaureusetöö
